OL,3,CWarning of rising cases of
OL,4,Ctuberculosis in Harrow
OL,6,FHarrow's Department of Public Health
OL,7,Fis now in the process of developing a
OL,8,FTB action plan.
OL,10,FFrom January 2023 to December 2025, an
OL,11,Faverage of 105 people a year were
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with active TB in the
OL,13,Fborough.
OL,15,FOf the total number of incidents 58%
OL,16,Fhad been living in the UK for less
OL,17,Fthan a year.
OL,19,FThere are "significant inequalities"
OL,20,Fin how TB impacts residents, according
OL,21,Fto the Public Health Department.
OL,26,@{D@KOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
