OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1773668260
OL,3,CWarning of rising cases of
OL,4,Ctuberculosis in Harrow
OL,6,FTuberculosis is an infection that
OL,7,Fusually affects the lungs.
OL,9,FIt is a bacterial infection that's
OL,10,Fusually spread by inhaling tiny
OL,11,Fdroplets from the coughs or sneezes of
OL,12,Fan infected person.
OL,14,FTB is a serious condition that can be
OL,15,Ftreated with antibiotics but can still
OL,16,Fbe life threatening in some cases.
OL,18,FTB can affect any part of the body,
OL,19,Fincluding the glands, bones and
OL,20,Fnervous system.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
