PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1773668260
OL,3,CWarning of rising cases of
OL,4,Ctuberculosis in Harrow
OL,6,FThe main treatment for tuberculosis is
OL,7,Fto take antibiotics for at least 6
OL,8,Fmonths.
OL,10,FIf TB has spread to your brain, spinal
OL,11,Fcord or the area around your heart,
OL,12,Fyou may also need to take steroid
OL,13,Fmedicine for a few weeks.
OL,15,FIf you have TB but do not have
OL,16,Fsymptoms (latent TB) you usually need
OL,17,Fto take antibiotics for 3 to 6 months.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/6
